message.entry: Specify either event labels or an event labels variable.
Specify either event lengths or an event lengths variable.
Specify either event ends or an event ends variable.
''{0}'' name-value pair is only supported when the first input is a timetable.
First input must either be a timetable or it must be a datetime or duration vector.
''{0}'' must either be a scalar or a vector with the same number of elements as the height of the first input.
Specify either event lengths or event ends but not both.
Event labels or an event labels variable are not supported when the second input is a categorical.
第二个输入必须为有效的时间表行下标或分类向量。
{0} must not be in the list of EventDataVariables.
Event lengths variable must be a duration or calendarDuration column vector.
The number of elements in the labels categorical vector must be the same as the number of rows of the input timetable.
事件标签变量不能为 datetime、duration 或 calendarDuration 变量。
Event labels variable must be a column vector.
Event labels variable must not be a char variable. Use a string array instead.
Event labels variable must not be a nested tabular variable.
Event ends variable must be a datetime or duration column vector.
Event lengths variable must be a duration variable if the event table has duration rowtimes.
Event ends variable must be the same data type as the event table row times.
Event ends variable and row times must both have time zones, or must both be unzoned.
Timetable must have an event table assigned to the Events property.
The default label supplied to syncevents must be a scalar.

The event tables attached to the timetables cannot be automatically merged. Consider detaching the event tables and merging them separately. When the input timetables have different event tables attached to them, they are merged by outerjoin using the common variables as keys.
All event tables must have the same event labels variable, event lengths variable, and event ends variable.
无法加载已保存的事件表，因为它与此版本的 MATLAB 不兼容
无法加载已保存的 EventtableProperties，因为它与此版本的 MATLAB 不兼容
无法加载已保存的 eventfilter，因为它与此版本的 MATLAB 不兼容
在输入中指定一个变量以用作 ''{0}''。请使用正整数、变量名称或包含单个 true 值的逻辑向量。
In order to specify PreserveEventVariables, provide at least one of EventDataVariables, EventLabelsVariable, EventLengthsVariable, or EventEndsVariable.

Using extractevents and specifying PreserveEventVariables without assigning the second output to a workspace variable does not modify the input timetable.\nUse [et,tt] = extractevents(tt,...,EventDataVariables=datavars,PreserveEventVariables=tf).
当设置了 EventLengthsVariable 或 EventEndsVariable 时，事件表不允许运算 ''{0}''。
将函数 ''{0}'' 应用于事件标签变量 ''{1}'' 时生成了错误。
将函数 ''{0}'' 应用于事件长度变量 ''{1}'' 时生成了错误。
将函数 ''{0}'' 应用于事件结束变量 ''{1}'' 时生成了错误。
